recency_negative_binomial<-brm(
  bf(recency ~ time_period+0),
  data = no_na_recency,
  family=negbinomial(),
  prior=c(
          prior(uniform(0,150),class="b",lb=0,ub=150),
          prior(gamma(1,0.5),class="shape")),
  chains = CHAINS, warmup = WARMUP, iter = ITER, seed = BAYES_SEED,
  refresh = 0,
  cores=4,
  threads=threading(2)
)
